{"tid":1235101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長遠]要求泛民簽立會組成約章","createTime":"2019-06-17T05:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T11:49:07.000Z","uid":8687,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"858e7e77d3c22291e1dcfce8ec1be0ed4cb59672","tid":1235101,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:13:37.000Z","msg":"建制下下就話要文明，我地就用文明將佢地打倒<br />\n<br />\n推動七二前登記做選民係必然，但要令議會長遠有健康發展，改革係必然，但先要定大方向，我覺得可從幾點做目標<br />\n<br />\n連任次數<br />\n30 / 35 歲以下參選人比例<br />\n出選次序<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位巴打可以傾份約章出黎要泛民簽署，唔簽的話選民應慎重考慮投唔投比佢<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講議會冇用<br />\n我覺得宜家做乜野都可以有用"},{"pid":"a07028da373531922267039e8f9b073795f67791","tid":1235101,"uid":8687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb873e904bde65eaea28103928e7242e66131575","tid":1235101,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3847b71b327bd34b79c26ee6f3dfdd647816d97","tid":1235101,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b26e5bc0443c0ca49d0115567bf9aa769b10424","tid":1235101,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac